# PROJECT NAME:

CompanyIntel Flow – AI-Powered Company Data Extraction Engine

==============================================================================

1. PROJECT EXPLANATION
   ==============================================================================

CompanyIntel Flow is a fully automated AI-powered data enrichment system designed to transform a simple company name into verified business intelligence.

Unlike traditional scraping tools that rely on brittle selectors or static directories, this system leverages Large Language Models (LLMs) to perform contextual company research. It reads and cross-verifies publicly available information across multiple sources, then returns structured, reliable contact data in strict JSON format.

The solution is built entirely in **n8n**, using Google Sheets as both the input and output database. Users simply provide a list of company names, and the workflow automatically:

* Reads each company name
* Researches verified public contact information
* Cleans and validates structured AI output
* Writes enriched data into a final sheet

The result is a scalable, AI-driven “Company Name → Verified Contact Intelligence” pipeline.

This eliminates manual research, copy-paste work, and unreliable scraping scripts.

